'''Wyoming Writers, Inc.''' was formed in 1974 to form a network of writers within the state and help fledgling writers acquire publication. An annual writers convention is held in various locations within the state as well as a writing contest.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://trib.com/news/local/govt-and-politics/wyoming-writers-announce-winners/article_78b7b8ba-e950-58c1-85cd-b19d13fb060c.html|title=Wyoming Writers announce winners|last=staff|first=the Star-Tribune|work=Casper Star-Tribune Online|access-date=2017-12-06|language=en}}</ref>
